Class ButtonZone

  • java.lang.Object
    • vialab.SMT.PGraphicsDelegate
      • vialab.SMT.Zone
        • vialab.SMT.ButtonZone
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.util.EventListener, processing.core.PConstants

    public class ButtonZone
extends Zone
    ButtonZone is a simple button, that when touched calls the press[ButtonName](), or the pressImpl() function if ButtonZone is extended with an overridden pressImpl()
